OL,3,CJustice minister rules out appeal of
OL,4,Csex offender anonymity law
OL,6,FIt excludes the public from Crown
OL,7,FCourt rape cases and also provides
OL,8,Fanonymity for suspects in sexual
OL,9,Foffence cases up to the point of
OL,10,Fcharge.
OL,12,FThe legislation also set out that
OL,13,Fthose not subsequently charged would
OL,14,Fhave anonymity for their lifetime and
OL,15,Ffor 25 years after their death.
OL,17,FMedia organisations launched a legal
OL,18,Fchallenge against some sections of the
OL,19,FAct, amid concern over the impact on
OL,20,Fthe reporting of sexual offence
OL,21,Fallegations.
