OL,3,CJustice minister rules out appeal of
OL,4,Csex offender anonymity law
OL,6,FAn example given was that the
OL,7,Flegislation would have prevented the
OL,8,Fmedia from being able to report the
OL,9,Fallegations against disgraced
OL,10,Fentertainer Jimmy Savile.
OL,12,FLast month, Mr Justice Humphreys
OL,13,Fstruck down parts of the Act which he
OL,14,Fsaid were beyond Stormont's
OL,15,Flegislative competence.
OL,17,FHe said the relevant sections were
OL,18,F"not law" and failed to strike a fair
OL,19,Fbalance between suspects' rights to
OL,20,Fprivacy and press freedom.
