OL,3,CJustice minister rules out appeal of
OL,4,Csex offender anonymity law
OL,6,FMs Long told the Assembly on Tuesday
OL,7,Fthat she had sought the views of her
OL,8,FExecutive colleagues on appealing the
OL,9,Fjudgment.
OL,11,FHowever, in an urgent written
OL,12,Fstatement to the Assembly on
OL,13,FWednesday, the Justice Minister
OL,14,Fconfirmed she would not appeal.
OL,16,FShe said legal advice she has received
OL,17,Fsaid that the ruling could have a
OL,18,F"substantial effect on Assembly
OL,19,Fprocesses for scrutinising its laws".
