OL,3,CJustice minister rules out appeal of
OL,4,Csex offender anonymity law
OL,6,FShe added: "Specifically, the judgment
OL,7,Fimposes a high standard of rationality
OL,8,Fupon the reasoning in Assembly and
OL,9,FCommittee debates during the passage
OL,10,Fof the legislation.
OL,12,F"This is a finding which imposes a
OL,13,Fstandard upon the legislative process
OL,14,Fwhich may be difficult to meet in
OL,15,Fpractice and which often cannot be
OL,16,Ffully captured by Hansard or committee
OL,17,Fminutes."
OL,19,FShe said she had raised the concerns
OL,20,Fraised in the legal advice with other
OL,21,FStormont ministers.
