OL,3,CJustice minister rules out appeal of
OL,4,Csex offender anonymity law
OL,6,FMs Long added: "I have now had an
OL,7,Fopportunity to consider their
OL,8,Fresponses which indicate that they do
OL,9,Fnot share my concerns about the wider
OL,10,Fimplications of the judgment.
OL,12,F"Given my only reason for considering
OL,13,Fan appeal was these wider implications
OL,14,Fto the Assembly, its departments and
OL,15,Fministers, I have decided not to
OL,16,Fproceed with an appeal."
